Cardi B Asks Fans for Advice on Her Pregnancy Line|http://www.elle.com|http://www.elle.com/culture/a23984701/cardi-b-pregnancy-line-advice-instagram/||2018-10-20|Ariana Yaptangco||Cardi B is continuing to keep things honest about motherhood. The rapper hopped on Instagram to ask fans for tips about the &#39;black line&#39; on her stomach following the birth of 3-month-old baby Kulture. The line starts above her bellybutton and ends just below, which Cardi showed as she posed in a black tracksuit. &quot;Ladies how do you guys get rid of the black line in the middle of your stomach after giving birth?? cause bitchðŸ˜’ðŸ˜’ðŸ˜’ðŸ˜’&quot; she wrote.

